gsplat
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Repository : https://github.com/nerfstudio-project/gsplat
License    : Apache License, Version 2.0
Copyright  : Copyright 2025 Nerfstudio Team

OpenGaussianSplatting uses gsplat as its core Gaussian rasterization backend
(rasterization, DefaultStrategy for densification/pruning).
The gsplat source code is NOT bundled in this repository; it is installed as
a runtime dependency via pip.

Full license text: https://github.com/nerfstudio-project/gsplat/blob/main/LICENSE

